# Framing

## head_shoulders
- **Short**: "head and shoulders"
- **Description**: head and shoulders framing, face occupies 40-60% of frame, tight crop showing head and upper shoulders
- **Camera Notes**: standard portrait framing, face is primary focus

## medium_shot
- **Short**: "medium shot"
- **Description**: medium shot from head to mid-torso, shows shoulders, neck, and partial torso, provides spatial context
- **Camera Notes**: wider framing, shows body posture and size relationships

## back_view
- **Short**: "back view"
- **Description**: camera positioned directly behind subject showing full back of head, neck, and shoulders, emphasizes hairstyle
- **Camera Notes**: pure back view, no face visible, best for hairstyle detail

## three_quarter_back
- **Short**: "three-quarter back view"
- **Description**: photographed from three-quarter back view, head turned slightly away from camera showing profile, emphasizes back-of-head hairstyle while showing side of face
- **Camera Notes**: 120-135 degree angle from frontal, shows both face profile and back hairstyle

## over_shoulder
- **Short**: "over-the-shoulder look back"
- **Description**: looking back over shoulder toward camera with soft genuine smile, photographed from rear three-quarter angle, shows both face and back hairstyle
- **Camera Notes**: rear three-quarter angle, subject looking back at camera

## side_profile
- **Short**: "side profile"
- **Description**: complete side profile view, woman facing 90° away from camera, shows full side silhouette
- **Camera Notes**: 90 degree angle, full side view, emphasizes profile features

## elevated_rear
- **Short**: "elevated rear view"
- **Description**: camera positioned above and behind showing clear top-down view of head and shoulders, emphasizes hairstyle from above
- **Camera Notes**: elevated angle looking down, shows top of head and hairstyle structure

---

## Smartphone & Snapchat Style

### intimate_close_up_pov
- **Short**: "intimate close-up POV selfie"
- **Description**: Extremely close-up smartphone selfie, very intimate POV framing, face and upper chest filling frame, personal private message feeling, like authentic late-night snap
- **Camera Notes**: minimum focus distance, natural phone perspective, intimate and personal

### high_angle_snapchat_selfie
- **Short**: "high-angle Snapchat selfie"
- **Description**: Classic Snapchat selfie with phone held slightly above and to side, slight high angle, looking up at camera, authentic mobile photography feel
- **Camera Notes**: arm extended overhead, natural phone perspective

### tilted_phone_angle
- **Short**: "tilted phone angle selfie"
- **Description**: Smartphone selfie with phone held at dramatic tilted/diagonal angle, creating dynamic off-balance composition, energetic casual vibe
- **Camera Notes**: rotated frame, authentic candid smartphone photography

### pov_front_flash
- **Short**: "POV with front flash"
- **Description**: Point-of-view selfie with front flash, subject directly illuminated, background darker with shadow behind, authentic front-flash mobile photography aesthetic
- **Camera Notes**: harsh-but-flattering flash, clean subject separation from background

### relaxed_casual_phone
- **Short**: "relaxed casual phone angle"
- **Description**: Natural casual smartphone selfie angle, slightly off-center framing, imperfect composition, authentic everyday mobile photography feel
- **Camera Notes**: natural phone positioning, not perfectly composed, authentic feel

---

## Polished Girlfriend Message

### clean_perfect_centered
- **Short**: "clean perfectly centered girlfriend photo"
- **Description**: Well-composed smartphone photo, perfectly centered framing, clean and polished appearance, intentional "message to boyfriend" composition, no casual imperfection
- **Camera Notes**: intentional composition, looks like carefully curated girlfriend message

### soft_daylight_girlfriend
- **Short**: "soft daylight girlfriend message"
- **Description**: Bright daytime selfie taken by window or in good lighting, clean polished look, soft natural lighting, authentic girlfriend sending photo to lover
- **Camera Notes**: well-lit, bright and clean appearance

### mirror_reflection_message
- **Short**: "mirror reflection girlfriend message"
- **Description**: Photo taken in mirror or reflective surface showing her thinking about you, natural authentic "just took this because I'm thinking of you" moment, clean but candid feel
- **Camera Notes**: mirror visible, natural authentic moment but polished










